Name: Nauman Sait
Notes: Winner of SEASON 6 : HELL DOWN UNDER. Won total prize money of Rs. 3,62,000 and A Hero Honda Karizma, Voted out in the 4th episode, re-entered in 7th episode defeating Pradeep in Zorb Task. Nauman defeated Lonkiri in finals.

Name: Longkiri Timung (Kiri)
Notes: Runner-up. Won a Hero Honda Karizma, Evicted in the 7th episode by challenge from Sufi in Ladder Task. Brought back in 13th episode by vote-in from the fellow contestants, where he defeated Sufi and Natasha in Plank Task. Lost to Nauman in the finals.

Name: Gurmeet Kaur Johal (Palak)
Notes: Won A Hero Honda Karizma, Voted out in the 3rd episode, re-entered in 7th episode defeating Bobby in Mechanical Bull task. Evicted by Longkiri in semi final task.

Name: Natasha Sinha
Notes: Voted out in the 11th episode. Brought back in 13th episode but failed in Plank task.

Name: Puneet Malhotra (Sufi)
Notes: Won A Hero Honda Karizma, Voted out in the 1st episode, re-entered in 7th episode defeating Longkiri in Ladder task. Voted out in the 10th episode. Brought back in 13th episode but failed in Plank task
